snippet.title: Hazel Kate Quinn
snippet.description:
I am doing some renovating.  Making some new videos to replace older ones, with newer, fresher perspectives for how to survive narcissistic abuse.  Again, I am only one of millions who have dealt with this.  Narcissistic abuse survivors are everywhere, from Hollywood to around the corner from you. 
I am no doctor or therapist, so I don't claim to have all answers. I'm a work in progress, like all of us are, no matter how long we've been on any path of recovery.  All of us want to live happy, healthy lives and while it takes work, it isn't impossible.  Narcissistic(or "Narc" for short) abuse has many layers, and none of it is easy.  It's not something anyone can just "snap out of."  But we can embrace better things as we walk away from what doesn't work for us anymore.  Music is one of the ways that helps me, so often you will see music videos here as well.  Healing  is possible from any kind of abuse, addiction, other trauma or mental illness.  Namaste!!!
